<h1 class='property-title'>border-top-right-radius</h1>
<p class='property-description'>The <code>border-top-right-radius</code> CSS property sets the rounding of the top-right corner of the element. The rounding can be a circle or an ellipse, or if one of the value is <code>0</code> no rounding is done and the corner is square.</p>